<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Visit Scheduled</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header {
      background: #4F46E5;
      color: white;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 0 0 15px 0;
    }
    .info-box {
      background: #f9fafb;
      border-left: 4px solid #4F46E5;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .info-box ul {
      margin: 10px 0 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
    }
    .info-box li {
      margin: 8px 0;
    }
    .info-box strong {
      color: #4F46E5;
      display: inline-block;
      width: 100px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #4F46E5;
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background: #4338CA;
    }
    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>ðŸ“… Visit Scheduled</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{familyMemberName}},</p>

      <p>A visit has been scheduled for <strong>{{clientName}}</strong>.</p>

      <div class="info-box">
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Date:</strong> {{visitDate}}</li>
          <li><strong>Time:</strong> {{visitTime}}</li>
          <li><strong>Caregiver:</strong> {{caregiverName}}</li>
          <li><strong>Duration:</strong> {{duration}}</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <p>You can view visit details and track progress in the family portal.</p>

      <div class="button-container">
        <a href="{{portalUrl}}/visits/{{visitId}}" class="button">View Visit Details</a>
      </div>

      <p>If you have any questions, please contact us or reply to this email.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br><strong>{{agencyName}}</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated notification from {{agencyName}}.</p>
      <p>You can manage your notification preferences in the <a href="{{portalUrl}}/settings">family portal settings</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
